{%- comment -%}
  Product card dispatcher.

  Every section renders product cards through this snippet
  (`{% render 'product-card', product: product %}`). It picks the card style
  from the theme setting "Product card style" (Online Store → Themes →
  Customize → Theme settings → Product cards):

    - "domaine" (default) → snippets/domaine-product-card.liquid
                            (interactive: swatches, hover image, sale badge)
    - "basic"             → snippets/product-card-basic.liquid
                            (simple image / title / price)

  Adding a new card style is a two-step change: create the snippet, then add it
  to the select in config/settings_schema.json and to the branch below.

  Accepts:
  - product {Object} - the product to render
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign style = settings.product_card_style | default: 'domaine'

  case style
    when 'basic'
      render 'product-card-basic', product: product
    else
      render 'domaine-product-card', product: product
  endcase
-%}
